<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 03:14:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>财新PMI显示中国8月份服务业活动扩张放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-expansion-slows-august-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-09-04/</link><description>周三的一项私营部门调查显示，尽管夏季旅游高峰，但中国服务业活动的增长在八月份放缓，促使一些公司因担心成本上升而裁员。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 01:49:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-expansion-slows-august-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-09-04/</guid></item><item><title>由于增长担忧重新浮现，股市和石油下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-04/</link><description>亚洲股市和全球股票期货周三暴跌，而油价触及数月低点，原因是华尔街科技股大幅抛售以及对美国经济增长的担忧重新抬头，促使投资者撤离风险资产。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 00:47:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-04/</guid></item><item><title>马尼拉称，菲律宾逃亡前市长在印度尼西亚被捕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fugitive-ex-mayor-philippines-arrested-indonesia-manila-says-2024-09-04/</link><description>马尼拉司法部周三在一份声明中表示，一名被指控与中国犯罪集团有联系的菲律宾逃亡前市长已在印度尼西亚被捕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 00:34:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fugitive-ex-mayor-philippines-arrested-indonesia-manila-says-2024-09-04/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，本已昂贵的全球房价将因降息而小幅提振</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/already-expensive-global-house-prices-get-modest-boost-rate-cuts-2024-09-04/</link><description>路透社对分析师的调查显示，由于预期抵押贷款利率将进一步下降，并有助于小幅提高昂贵房产的承受能力，今年和明年大多数主要市场的房价将小幅上涨。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 00:22:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/already-expensive-global-house-prices-get-modest-boost-rate-cuts-2024-09-04/</guid></item><item><title>美国安全专员呼吁对 Shein 和 Temu 进行调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-safety-commissioners-call-investigation-into-shein-temu-2024-09-03/</link><description>美国消费品安全委员会网站周二发布的一封信称，美国消费品安全委员会的两位领导人呼吁该机构对电子商务零售商 Shein 和 Temu 进行调查，因为这两个网站上销售了“致命的婴幼儿产品”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 23:27:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-safety-commissioners-call-investigation-into-shein-temu-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>萨巴伦卡连续第四次晋级美国公开赛半决赛，弗里茨和纳瓦罗让主场球迷高兴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/fritz-navarro-delight-us-open-home-crowd-roar-into-semi-finals-2024-09-03/</link><description>阿琳娜·萨巴伦卡连续第四次闯入美国公开赛半决赛，而美国选手泰勒·弗里茨和艾玛·纳瓦罗则在阿瑟·阿什体育场首次进入四强，让主场观众感到高兴。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 23:09:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/fritz-navarro-delight-us-open-home-crowd-roar-into-semi-finals-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：增长担忧、科技股低迷带来九月忧郁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-03/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:49:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>白宫要求各机构加强互联网路由安全工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/white-house-asks-agencies-step-up-internet-routing-security-efforts-2024-09-03/</link><description>面对美国官员对中国转移互联网流量能力的担忧，白宫周二表示，希望联邦机构加强网络上的互联网路由安全。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 18:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/white-house-asks-agencies-step-up-internet-routing-security-efforts-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪否认暂停墨西哥工厂计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-denies-report-pause-mexico-plant-plans-2024-09-03/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪周二表示，它没有推迟有关墨西哥工厂计划的“任何决定”，并否认了当天早些时候的报道。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 18:20:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-denies-report-pause-mexico-plant-plans-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国承诺鼓励对尼日利亚投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/nigeria-china-sign-economic-nuclear-energy-pact-2024-09-03/</link><description>两国领导人在北京会面后，中国誓言鼓励更有“实力”的企业到尼日利亚投资，而尼日利亚则表示对中国企业建设工厂、开发能源和矿产资源持开放态度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 16:57:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/nigeria-china-sign-economic-nuclear-energy-pact-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国海绿能源与合作伙伴将投资22亿美元建设西班牙绿色氢能项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/chinas-hygreen-energy-partners-invest-22-bln-spanish-green-hydrogen-projects-2024-09-03/</link><description>中国电解槽制造商Hygreen Energy周二表示，其及其合作伙伴将在西班牙南部安达卢西亚地区的绿色氢项目上投资超过20亿欧元（22.1亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 16:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/chinas-hygreen-energy-partners-invest-22-bln-spanish-green-hydrogen-projects-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>纽约州州长 Hochul 前助手 Linda Sun 被控充当中国代理人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/ex-aide-ny-governor-hochul-charged-with-acting-chinese-agent-2024-09-03/</link><description>纽约州州长凯西·霍赫尔(Kathy Hochul)的一名前助手周二被指控秘密充当中国政府的代理人，以换取数百万美元的赔偿和礼物，其中包括美味鸭肉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 15:51:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/ex-aide-ny-governor-hochul-charged-with-acting-chinese-agent-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>安哥拉权衡中国和欧洲的竞争对手融资以转型经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/angola-weighs-rival-china-european-financing-bids-transform-economy-2024-09-03/</link><description>安哥拉财政部长周二表示，如果安哥拉要吸收更多从太阳能电池板到电动汽车等中国制造的产品，中国需要加大对安哥拉的融资力度，因为这位前欧佩克成员国正在考虑争夺来自北京和欧洲的投标。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 10:41:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/angola-weighs-rival-china-european-financing-bids-transform-economy-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>研究人员称，美国选民受到中国网络影响力的攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-voters-targeted-by-chinese-influence-online-researchers-say-2024-09-03/</link><description>情报公司 Graphika 的最新研究显示，中国的社交媒体影响力行动正在冒充美国选民，诋毁美国政客，并在 11 月 5 日美国总统大选之前传播分裂信息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 10:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-voters-targeted-by-chinese-influence-online-researchers-say-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>“香港47”：法院结束香港最大国家安全案件的减刑听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-47-court-wraps-up-mitigation-hearing-citys-largest-national-security-2024-09-03/</link><description>周二，最后一批 45 名香港活动人士在一次具有里程碑意义的国家安全审判中提出了最后的减刑请求，罪名是“阴谋颠覆国家政权”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 04:53:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-47-court-wraps-up-mitigation-hearing-citys-largest-national-security-2024-09-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>